stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Requested

    state "Launch pipeline" as Pipeline {
        Requested --> Generating
        Generating --> Deploying: spec valid
        Deploying --> Injecting: LXC ready
        Injecting --> Verifying: files applied
        Verifying --> LaunchPassed: checks pass

        Generating --> LaunchFailed: generation error
        Deploying --> LaunchFailed: deploy error
        Injecting --> LaunchFailed: inject error
        Verifying --> LaunchFailed: verification error
    }

    LaunchPassed --> Active: persist active
    LaunchFailed --> Destroyed: cleanup

    Active --> Completed: correct flag
    Active --> Expired: TTL reached
    Active --> Destroyed: cleanup request
    Completed --> Destroyed: later cleanup
    Expired --> Destroyed: reaper cleanup
    Destroyed --> [*]

    note right of Pipeline
        Pipeline states are transient
        SSE progress stages.
    end note

    note right of Active
        Active, completed, expired,
        and destroyed are stored
        challenge statuses.
    end note
